Yesterday we showed you Pete’s flight pack ready for his first IFR flight on the aircraft. Here he is on that very flight, taxing out to holding point November ready to take to the skies for the first time full IFR.
The flight went well, with Pete departing to NEDUL then right towards THRED then tracking back to the BIA for some NDB hold training, procedural NDB and ILS approaches.
Pete and Alex are now in the sim working on RNAV approaches and flight appreciation. Catch up with us later to find out more.
